name: UFO_001
description: Part of a series of drawings based on imagined encounters with multi-dimensional crafts.  The original drawing was scanned and auto-traced into a vector drawing that was drawn onto Yupo paper using an Axidraw plotter. The watercolor washes were applied to a matrix of 24 drawings. Each one will be sold individually and once all are posted the original drawing and matrix will be minted as NFTs.
